		*** View Children
		
	
	-->	ViewChildren is most used decorator and has many important use cases.
	
	-->	We can use @viewChildren to inject a reference to a query list of a component or DOM Element.
	
	-->	@viewChildren gets loaded after ngAfterViewInit() method.
		-- Don't try this onInit
	
	
	-->	ViewChildren is very similar to viewChild but only difference is that viewChild will get you one element whereas viewChildren will get you an list of component and DOM Element.
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
